<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00521/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>Site-CN-06地下停车场的A-155号车位，任何车辆在该车位停放超过48小时后，其油箱内的燃料将被转换为原油。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-06地下停车场<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>于Site-CN-06地下停车场，已添置路障和警告标志<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>修车费可以报销一下吗？</em>——Dr.Jackson</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00521" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00521" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00521-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4546338&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247393" alt="miku1314" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4546338)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;">miku1314</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1610198635 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">09 Jan 2021 13:23</span></p>
